<p>

<b><it>Higher Learning</it></b> is a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../658/34658.xml">
1995</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../089/8089.xml">
drama film</link>, starring an <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../601/232601.xml">
ensemble cast</link>. It also featured <celebrity wordnetid="109903153" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<host wordnetid="110187130" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
<supermodel wordnetid="110676319" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../613/236613.xml">
Tyra Banks</link></supermodel>
</host>
</celebrity>
' first performance in a theatrical <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../571/10571.xml">
movie</link>.</p>
<p>

Laurence Fishburne won an <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../024/476024.xml">
Image Award</link> for "Outstanding Supporting Actor in a Motion Picture" for his performance; Ice Cube was also nominated for the award.</p>
<p>

<university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<ranking wordnetid="114429484" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../765/37765.xml">
UCLA</link></ranking>
</university>
 filled in for the college, Columbus University. The exterior shots and outdoor scenes were shot on the campus.</p>
<p>

In addition to "Higher", performed by Ice Cube, the soundtrack includes performances of newer material (at the time) by <group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
